<title>USA: EAI to make 3D children's coloring games.</title>
<headline>EAI to make 3D children's coloring games.</headline>
<dateline>AMES, Iowa 1997-01-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Engineering Animation Inc said Tuesday it will produce a series of four Crayola three-dimensional interactive products to be published by International Business Machines Corp.</p>
<p>The first product will be the Magic 3D Coloring Book, allowing children to color their own three dimensional scenes. The product, which  uses technology developed for high-end graphics workstations, is planned to be available in retail stores in spring, EAI said.</p>
<p>EAI specializes in applied three-dimensional visualization technology.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
